  "summary": "This agreement outlines a joint venture between Veoneer and Nissin for the development of specific ventures (VNBJ and VNBZ). The agreement specifies Japanese law governs the agreement, with indemnification obligations for D&O liability imposed on the non-operator (Acme Holdings) before the JV closing.  The amendment to the agreement is contingent upon the closing of two separate agreements (VNBJ SPA and VNBZ SPA), and if these agreements are terminated, the amendment will be null and void.",
